{
  "stem": "13817.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then from there, the coal would be sent into Germany most probably or the-- or even to-- around there there were different camps, which were working on war industry.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There again, the food was a little better than before, but still not enough to survive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You would get the tar coffee in the morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You would get the water soup, which was a little bit thicker, sometimes was a vegetable and a potato in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You would get this two or three slices of bread every day and the soup at night and before we went to work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then-- and then noontime, when we were in the camp, we would sleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would come back to camp about 7 o'clock or 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would let us sleep 'til about noon, and that was the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we would be-- have to work in the camp building, enlarging it, cleaning it, all different things [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We would be marched to the-- to the coal mine with the SS guards around us and they would use their back of the guns to pick you or push you.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there again, we wouldn't get enough food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Luckily, the-- these miners were living in the country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were raising chickens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were-- had-- had little garden plots or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't have much, but they had extra food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't have any clothing, for instance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To get extra food, I would sell my second uniform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I would come out of the-- of the mine and I would tell-- I would go down with two uniforms on and would sell him one.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He would dye the uniform, use it as underwear, use it as outerwear too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The women would alterate it a little bit.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
